==Japanese==
{{janoun|かたかな|katakana}}
#A set of [[Japanese]] [[syllabary]] [[characters]], secondary to [[hiragana]], derived from portions of Chinese characters whose sounds approximate the Japanese sound being represetned. Katakana is mostly used for transliteration from western languages.

